title: TI and Tiny The Family Hustle S03E13-18
description:
These seem to be the episodes that weren't uploaded last year. I cannot find episode 11 ANYWHERE! If I do I will upload it.
 The season was divided up into 2 parts - Vol 1 and Vol 2. hence the dual episode numbers.

Episode 12/Ep 5
 White for a Day
 Released Sep 02, 2013
 Fed up with Shekinah always saying she wants to be white, Tameka suggests they spend the day doing things white people do. But will Shekinah see that the grass isn't always greener?

Episode 13/Ep 6
 Who's the Better Driver?
 Released Sep 09, 2013
 After attending their first NASCAR event, Tip and Tameka argue over who's the better driver. With each of their personal cars on the line, the whole family joins in on the competition

Episode 14/Ep 7
 Ringmasters
 Released Sep 16, 2013
 King, Major, and Precious are hired for their first paid gig at the circus. Under pressure, will the kids step up to the challenge and put on a great performance?

Episode 15/Ep8
 The Workout Video
 Released Sep 23, 2013
 Tameka and Shekinah decide to make a unique workout video for people who don't like to work out. But with both women having different ideas, can they get it together in time? Meanwhile, Tip takes the boys to LA for some business and pleasure.

Episode 16/Ep 9
 Education First
 Released Sep 30, 2013
 When Domani and King come home with less than stellar report cards, Tip takes matters into his own hands and hires them a tutor. Meanwhile, Tameka prepares her new girl group French Kiss for their first paid gig.

Episode 17/Ep 10
 Back On Tour
 Released Oct 07, 2013
 As Tip heads out for the first leg of his two-month long nationwide tour with Lil' Wayne, the kids aren't ready for him to go and convince him to let them come.

Episode 18/Ep 11
 Family Fun Time
 Released Oct 14, 2013
 In the third season finale, Tip decides to take the family to Puerto Rico for a much needed getaway. Meanwhile, Tameka meets up with Niq Niq and the OMG Girlz as they embark on their newest tour.
